{"tid":1556892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔開心","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:40:47.000Z","uid":179805,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"baefb9e70c589d52804fc1f2afcaa26b70f059e0","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:08:25.000Z","msg":"真係好唔開心<br />\n我唔奢求呢篇文可以改變呢場運動好多<br />\n不過都多謝大家入嚟<br />\n<br />\n我知大家應該都好攰<br />\n尤其開咗學多咗嘢做<br />\n但我想大家睇一張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4q2rWGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4q2rWGb.jpg&h=ad0fcde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得呢張圖<br />\n林鄭講話撤回<br />\n已經有一批人唔再理呢場運動<br />\n而其他人都開始放軟手腳<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家唔好忘記<br />\n我地有幾多手足以死明志<br />\n又有幾多手足畀狗拉咗<br />\n幾多手足畀狗毒打 非禮<br />\n你唔信強姦同831有死人都好<br />\n上面果啲都一定係事實<br />\n<br />\n好多人都話文宣少咗<br />\n其實我覺得係大家分享少咗<br />\n可能大家都習慣去tg睇消息<br />\n但係唔好忘記 有批人係唔用tg<br />\n甚至連登都唔用 淨係用ig之類<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n當初616 818 點解咁多人出嚟？<br />\n除咗因為民陣個名<br />\n我記得 仲因為有好多手足去派傳單<br />\n我跪求大家<br />\n分享多啲文宣圖 印多啲update嘅文宣貼上牆<br />\n就算係和理非 都可以做翻多少少<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係想大家行多一步</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只係想大家行翻退後咗果步</span><br />\n<br />\n我暫時搵到咁多有關行動嘅圖<br />\n希望各位手足可以搵多少少<br />\n喺度分享之餘<br />\n再分享去其他po<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtTKJpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtTKJpH.jpg&h=384e8544&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Apggzwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApggzwn.jpg&h=a611d123&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOouUwo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOouUwo.jpg&h=2df8bd8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47da9c58e018c14faf2b8c975e39f405f7090984","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"6c06d885e772bb3f5da79af801483d49983e1814","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"我打漏咗<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記<br />\n仲有畀人斬嘅手足"},{"pid":"2de2c747eff52619089d48945dea757ca00d1d10","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"776fe68d00081b50959f0412e58bdd9312e81c01","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"5f97bd824103c6761a6d8c7ae2116966f84809f0","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:10:07.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"20c9b4a85542db5a74e40bef627eb1359a107221","tid":1556892,"uid":146737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:10:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=1c0d3824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"116b136084058fe2177b6ea6e6f7e24c026fa548","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"bbd57ebe6fe5138ba9e3a4101ff327739dff8bd6","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0