30501da126d1bda70f2860e4be44bb1bfc1","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"多謝大家幫手推po"},{"pid":"8352cdc274e583e850d7272155a2d3f0f2eaf85f","tid":1556892,"uid":179805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"我個人嚟講<br />\n我由一個終極和理非<br />\n變做一個會幫手搞啲和理非活動嘅和理非<br />\n我知唔係每個人都再行前到多一步<br />\n但至少<br />\n如果退後咗嘅手足<br />\n行翻前退後咗果步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}